A)  TO PROMOTE THE BENEFIT OF THE PUBLIC ESPECIALLY THE BENGALI COMMUNITY IN THE UK AND ABROAD WITHOUT DISTINCTION OF SEX, RACE, RELIGION, POLITICAL  OR OTHER OPINIONS, BY ASSOCIATING TOGETHER WITH THE PUBLIC AND VOLUNTARY ORGANISATIONS IN A COMMON EFFORT TO ADVANCE EDUCATION AND TO PROVIDE FACILITIES FOR RECREATION AND OTHER  LEISURE-TIME OCCUPATION IN THE INTERESTS OF SOCIAL WELFARE WITH THE OBJECT OF IMPROVING THE CONDITIONS OF LIFE OF SUCH PERSONS;   
