(C)  PROMOTE SUCH OTHER CHARITABLE PURPOSES AS MAY FROM TIME TOTIME BE DETERMINED. 
THE ASSOCIATION SHALL BE NON-PARTY IN POLITICS AND NON-SECTARIAN IN RELIGION. THE AREA OF BENEFIT SHALL BE FOR THE BENEFIT OF EVERYONE LIVING IN WALKER, AND ESPECIALLY THOSE LIVING IN THE HEXHAM AVENUE HOUSING ESTATE.

