THE PURPOSES OF THE SCHOOL ARE AS FOLLOWS:

TO ADVANCE THE EDUCATION OF THE PUBLIC IN THE CHINESE LANGUAGE, ART AND CULTURE IN PARTICULAR BUT NOT EXCLUSIVELY BY THE RUNNING OF A SCHOOL IN NEWCASTLE UPON TYNE WITH THE AIM TO CONTRIBUTE TO IMPROVED RACIAL HARMONY, EQUALITY AND DIVERSITY IN THE NORTH EAST OF ENGLAND.

